        public void waitFor()
             throws InterruptedException,
                    IOException
        Waits for the process to execute, returning the command output taken from the profile's execution.
        抛出:
        InterruptedException - if we are interrupted while waiting for the process to launch
        IOException - if there is a problem with reading the input stream of the launching process

      • waitFor

        public void waitFor(long timeout)
             throws InterruptedException,
                    IOException
        Waits for the process to execute, returning the command output taken from the profile's execution.
        参数:
        timeout - the maximum time to wait in milliseconds
        抛出:
        InterruptedException - if we are interrupted while waiting for the process to launch
        IOException - if there is a problem with reading the input stream of the launching process

      • getConsoleOutput

        public String getConsoleOutput()
                        throws IOException
        Gets all console output of the binary. Output retrieval is non-destructive and non-blocking.
        返回:
        the console output of the executed binary.
        抛出:
        IOException - IO exception reading from the output stream of the firefox process
